    "description": "Kumarakom Lake Resort Holdings Services is actively seeking a talented and motivated Reservation Manager to join our dynamic team in Meerut. This is an excellent opportunity for professionals who are passionate about making a real impact in a fast-growing organization.\n\nAbout Kumarakom Lake Resort Holdings Services:\nKumarakom Lake Resort Holdings Services is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Handle guest complaints and resolve issues promptly\n• Plan and execute banquets, events, and MICE functions\n• Coordinate housekeeping and maintenance for room readiness\n• Deliver exceptional guest experiences in line with brand standards\n• Manage front office operations including check-in/check-out\n• Prepare daily operating reports and present to management\n• Manage procurement of hotel supplies and control operating costs\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Master's degree preferred\n• 10-15 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in F&B Service\n• Proficiency in Revenue Management\n• Proficiency in Travel Management\n• Proficiency in Sommelier Skills\n• Proficiency in PMS Systems\n• Proficiency in Yield Management\n• Proficiency in Event Management\n• Proficiency in Crisis Management\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Salary Range: 20 LPA - 40 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Meerut, Uttar Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Kumarakom Lake Resort Holdings Services!",
